	<summary>
	6/5/2008--Introduced.<br/>Entitles a member of the uniformed services to additional pay of $1,500 per month while the member's service is extended, or eligibility for retirement is suspended, by the exercise of any provision of law commonly referred to as a &quot;stop-loss authority.&quot;<br/>
	</summary>
